nordstrom marshall fields and the federated allied and carter 
hawley hale chains and designers oscar de la renta dana buchman 
linda allard and bill blass 
we believe that ivory must be kept out of fashion and in the 
possession of the magnificent creatures for whom it was originally 
designed those firms said why should a baby elephant be 
orphaned for a few bangles and beads 
