the legislation would bring into line with supreme court rulings 
existing federal law that calls for the death penalty for offenses 
including murder treason espionage air piracy and certain deaths 
involving explosives 
the bill would for the first time authorize the death penalty 
for attempts to assassinate the president murder by a federal 
