home as opposition mounts and a refugee exodus continues 
krenz is by far the youngest official on the 21member politburo 
dominated by aging communists many of them in their 70s but he 
has a reputation for following honeckers hardline stance 
a burly bushyhaired man krenz for long has been plagued by 
rumors he was an alcoholic although there has been virtually 
nothing to substantiate that 
he is known for his spontaneous visits to local bars and 
restaurants that are the bane of his bodyguards 
krenz was born the son of a tailor in kolberg a coastal town in 
what is now northwestern poland on march 19 1937 
he joined the fdj communist youth organization in 1953 while he 
was still in high school and east germany was only four years old 
krenz studied to be a teacher but joined the east german army 
and rose to the rank of lieutenant before being discharged in 1959 
after studying in moscow from 1964 to 1967 krenz returned to 
become a leading official of the communist youth organization in 
east germany 
he has been a member of the communist partys central committee 
since 1973 and joined the ruling politburo 10 years later 
in recent years he has been in charge of the communist youth 
organizations and internal security officials while many 
acknowledged he was being groomed to take over from honecker 
