highway 101 to her home in san francisco 
it was like bumper cars she said it literally started to 
buckle bend and bounce cars were bounced into the air on the 
roadway cars tried to stop but the motion kept them running even 
if you slammed on the brakes 
cars slammed into each other and into guardrails and stopped 
one woman rolled down her window and asked if she had car problems 
i said no its not your car its an earthquake 
